StringValues.16: The Stave of Palenqual, an Aun Tumerok relic. This magic caster was given to the Aun xuta by spirits called the Deru. It is the embodiment of Marae Lassel's spirit - a single great totem for the island as a whole. Three Tumerok fetishes are attached to this weapon; those of Timaru, Siraluun, and Tonk.
